import React from 'react'

import {
    FormControl,
    FormLabel,
    FormHelperText,
    Input,
    Center
} from '@chakra-ui/react'  

const AddRecipe = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <Form>
          <Field name='name'>
            {({ field, form }) => (
              <FormControl isInvalid='gotta put a name'>
                <FormLabel>First name</FormLabel>
                <Input {...field} placeholder='name' />
                <FormErrorMessage>{form.errors.name}</FormErrorMessage>
              </FormControl>
            )}
          </Field>
          <Button
            mt={4}
            colorScheme='teal'
            isLoading={props.isSubmitting}
            type='submit'
          >
            Submit
          </Button>
        </Form>
    </>
    )
}

export default AddRecipe
